{{else if eq .Level "elementary"}}
- When/why questions about story events
- Simple character motivations
- Basic inferences from explicit information
{{else if eq .Level "intermediate"}}
- Character feelings and motivations
- Cause and effect relationships
- Moderate inferences requiring some reasoning
{{else if eq .Level "upper_intermediate"}}
- Complex inferences and predictions
- Character relationships and conflicts
- Thematic elements and symbolism (if present)
{{else}}
- Deep analysis of themes, motifs, and character development
- Cultural and historical context questions
- Advanced literary analysis
{{end}}

**Language Level Guidelines:**
{{if eq .Level "beginner"}}
- Simple sentence structures
- Basic vocabulary
- Clear, direct questions
{{else if eq .Level "elementary"}}
- Some compound sentences
- Common vocabulary
- Questions that require basic reasoning
{{else if eq .Level "intermediate"}}
- Complex sentence structures
- Varied vocabulary
- Questions requiring inference and analysis
{{else if eq .Level "upper_intermediate"}}
- Advanced grammar and vocabulary
- Questions requiring critical thinking
- Cultural context awareness
{{else}}
- Sophisticated language use
- Deep analytical questions
- Cultural and literary nuance
{{end}}

**Output Format:**
Return a JSON array of question objects, each with this exact structure:
